snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Khumar Episode 11 [Eng Sub] Digitally Presented by Happilac Paints - Feroze Khan - Neelam Muneer - 29th December 2023 - Har Pal Geo

Khumar Digitally Presented by Happilac Paints

Khumar is a timeless love story that delves into the challenges arising from societal class differences and the negativity that stems from them. Khumar explores the complexities of love in the face of societal expectations and challenges. Faiz and Hareem, two individuals from different backgrounds, find their lives connected by destiny.

Faiz, born into an affluent family, contrasts sharply with Hareem, who hails from a
lower-middle-class background. Despite their differences, fate weaves their paths together. Hareem, diligently working to make ends meet amid her brother Rufi's educational needs and her mother's medical expenses, faces numerous hurdles. In the midst of her struggles, Faiz, a friend of Rufi's, silently supports them financially and even gets work for Hareem, albeit discreetly.

Hareem's family doesn't know that Faiz loves her, leading to a one-sided love affair. Faiz's love for Hareem remains a secret, but his mother disapproves of his association with Hareem's family due to the significant class difference. But fate decides to play its tune, and an unexpected event turns the lives of Faiz and Hareem upside down.

What was this surprising turn of events that changed everything for Faiz and Hareem? Will the gap in their social status keep them apart? Can Faiz convince his mother to accept Hareem? If they marry, can they create a happy life together despite their different backgrounds and mindsets?

7th Sky Entertainment Presentation 
Producers: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi 
Writer: Maha Malik
Director: Ali Faizan

Cast:
Feroze Khan as Faiz
Neelam Muneer as Hareem
Hina Bayat as Kehkasha Begum
Asma Abbas as Durdana
Behroz Sabzwari as Sheikh Furqan
Zainab Qayoom as Dil Araa
Shehryar Zaidi as Taufeeq
Adnan Samad as Nasir
Sheherzade Peerzada as Hamna  
Minsa Malik as Laiba 
Kinza Malik as Atiya
Mehmood Akhtar as Zaawar  
Agha Mustafa as Rayyan  
Hamzah Tariq as Rufi
Ayesha Rajpoot as Shagufta
Mizna Waqas as Husna
Sohail Masood as Mirza Sahab
Birjees Farooqui as Salma

Episode 3967: Chit Uthao
--------------------------------------------------------
Tapu Sena has devised an outstanding Christmas strategy in which each Gokuldham member must give a gift to each other. Each member will be able to pick their giving partner anonymously, according to the idea. Tapu Sena arrives at everyone's residence and pairs them up with a companion, but they are not permitted to divulge their names. They will bring the present wrapped in red paper on Christmas Day, as per the rules. Watch the episode to find out what happens in Tapu Sena's unusual Christmas game!

snippet.title: New Holland 5500 Jumped in Canal working Time Rotavator in Field | Rice Farming | Pramod's Life
snippet.description:
LIKE || SHARE || SUBSCRIBE
========================
Story :- My New Holland 5500 Tractor with 6.5 feet Rotavator Mistakenly Jumped in Canal while working in the field but at that we had 2 more tractor Mahindra Arjun NOVO 605 di-i 4x4 tractor the 9 tines cultivator which also comes with us for cultivation in the field and another one is Mahindra 275 Di XP Plus Tractor with 7 Tines another cultivator which was far from place we are so we called our nearest Tractor to help us and pulling it out from the canal water but after so much tries we failed so finally we call a JCB 3dx Xpert Backhoe Loader help us Puling out our tractor from this canal in this incident we just lost all the oils in the tractor and filters 
thanks for watching please do subscribe and hit the like button 
#tractorvideos #farmingvideos #JCBvideos

About The Show:
----------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a comedy show inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada Family which consists of uneducated businessmen Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal‚Äôs Wife Daya & their naughty Son Tipendra Gada living in 'Gokuldham Co-operative Society' and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. In case of a problem and emergency, Jethalal Gada often rushes to Taarak Mehta to seek his help and guidance, as he finds a philosopher in him. The housing society residents help each other find solutions when facing common, real-life challenges and getting involved in sticky situations.
